00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:50,660
so some immortals can’t sit in nearby seats.

None
00:32:50,840 --> 00:32:53,500
If I arrange wrong seats for them,

None
00:32:53,940 --> 00:32:54,840
they may

None
00:32:55,260 --> 00:32:57,080
blame me

None
00:32:57,120 --> 00:32:58,700
some day.

None
00:32:59,260 --> 00:33:01,400
It’s obviously a hot potato.

None
00:33:02,260 --> 00:33:04,540
Give me some suggestions.

None
00:33:07,420 --> 00:33:08,580
I have a good idea.

None
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:11,100
How about exchanging our tasks?

None
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,900
You can preside at the wedding for me,

None
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:14,700
because I can’t witness their wedding

None
00:33:14,700 --> 00:33:18,120
but do nothing for Xu Feng.

None
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:20,050
Moon Immortal,

None
00:33:21,090 --> 00:33:23,470
Heavenly Emperor assigned it to you but not me.

None
00:33:23,540 --> 00:33:25,520
Only you can do this.

None
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:27,240
Go for it.

None
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:33,080
Nobody can help me.

None
00:33:45,679 --> 00:33:46,659
Your Highness, you’re back.

None
00:33:47,380 --> 00:33:48,639
Is Fairy Jin Mi OK?

None
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:49,659
Yes.

None
00:33:53,239 --> 00:33:55,480
Heavenly Emperor ordered someone to send it here.

None
00:33:56,179 --> 00:33:58,239
He said this cup could turn water into tea.

None
00:33:59,360 --> 00:34:01,880
His Majesty said you always liked drinking tea

None
00:34:02,820 --> 00:34:04,699
and could do something others can’t do,

None
00:34:06,719 --> 00:34:09,500
so it’s very suitable for you

None
00:34:10,060 --> 00:34:11,960
and gave it to you as the wedding gift.

None
00:34:12,900 --> 00:34:13,699
Father,

None
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:15,580
your paternal love

None
00:34:16,300 --> 00:34:17,620
is too late.

None
00:34:18,600 --> 00:34:19,860
The irony is that

None
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:23,260
when I treated him with all my heart before,

None
00:34:24,900 --> 00:34:26,520
I gained nothing.

None
00:34:28,100 --> 00:34:31,460
But His Majesty still thinks highly of you.

None
00:34:35,640 --> 00:34:37,740
Because he finds

None
00:34:38,740 --> 00:34:40,140
I behave much like him,

None
00:34:41,700 --> 00:34:44,300
but I’m always his blemish left
after a night of romance.

None
00:34:45,640 --> 00:34:46,900
In his heart,

None
00:34:47,140 --> 00:34:49,960
there is always a much better son than me,

None
00:34:52,540 --> 00:34:53,540
Xu Feng.

None
00:34:54,920 --> 00:34:57,520
He is magnanimous, upright, open and aboveboard.

None
00:34:57,900 --> 00:35:00,220
He doesn’t need to play tricks

None
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:03,960
but can be praised by other immortals easily.

None
00:35:04,220 --> 00:35:07,020
As a man, he’s also jealous of Xu Feng,

None
00:35:09,480 --> 00:35:11,340
but, as a dad,

None
00:35:13,860 --> 00:35:16,140
he always favors Xu Feng in his heart.

None
00:35:17,240 --> 00:35:18,320
Your Highness,

None
00:35:19,940 --> 00:35:21,300
think it over.

None
00:35:21,640 --> 00:35:22,320
No need.

None
00:35:27,820 --> 00:35:29,820
I won’t waste

None
00:35:30,200 --> 00:35:31,760
the efforts I made these three years.

None
00:35:35,460 --> 00:35:37,420
Notify the Bird Family and
three-direction heaven troops.

None
00:35:42,560 --> 00:35:43,240
Yes.

None
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:08,920
Your Highness, the invisible sentry reports that

None
00:36:08,980 --> 00:36:10,420
the three-direction heaven troops
gather together secretly

None
00:36:10,420 --> 00:36:11,400
and the Bird Family also behaves abnormally recently.

None
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,720
It seems they’ll do something great.

None
00:36:15,200 --> 00:36:18,220
Run Yu seems to be ready to rebel.

None
00:36:19,420 --> 00:36:21,540
Your Highness, should we do something?

None
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:27,620
Let me think.

None
00:36:28,520 --> 00:36:30,810
"Sweet Spring"

None
00:37:16,660 --> 00:37:17,460
Jin Mi.

None
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:36,080
Wonderful.

None
00:37:38,520 --> 00:37:39,360
Yes.

None
00:37:40,200 --> 00:37:41,460
It’s tough and smooth.

None
00:37:42,420 --> 00:37:43,550
It’s glossy but not slippery.

None
00:37:44,140 --> 00:37:45,840
If you like it,

None
00:37:46,720 --> 00:37:48,240
I can present some to you.

None
00:37:49,140 --> 00:37:50,920
I mean, this poem is wonderful.

None
00:37:52,020 --> 00:37:54,080
Don’t write love poetry.

None
00:37:54,780 --> 00:37:57,120
I write my thoughts on the plain handkerchief.

None
00:37:57,600 --> 00:37:59,580
I read it again and again after writing it.

None
00:38:00,100 --> 00:38:02,700
It’s full of my worries,

None
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:06,860
but who knows it?

None
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:09,460
It’s so easy to understand,

None
00:38:10,920 --> 00:38:12,600
but who are you missing?

None
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:16,540
So it’s not easy enough to understand.

None
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:19,440
Yes.

None
00:38:20,580 --> 00:38:22,620
No only the handkerchief is made of fiber.

None
00:38:23,640 --> 00:38:26,280
Look at this piece of Xuan paper facing the light.

None
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:29,260
You’ll find it’s also made of fiber,

None
00:38:29,980 --> 00:38:32,960
but you refused me when I wanted
to present some to you just now.

None
00:38:34,400 --> 00:38:35,740
We haven’t met for three years.

None
00:38:37,720 --> 00:38:38,620
I thought

None
00:38:39,940 --> 00:38:41,560
you were still loath to meet me.

None
00:38:43,480 --> 00:38:46,680
In these three years, I think a lot.

None
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:49,100
I believe

None
00:38:51,440 --> 00:38:52,820
you didn’t kill Dad.

None
00:38:53,740 --> 00:38:57,620
Water Immortal’s death is indeed related to me,

None
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:04,180
but,

None
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:11,480
can you refuse to marry Run Yu?

None
00:39:12,420 --> 00:39:13,400
I’ll explain his death

None
00:39:14,460 --> 00:39:16,200
to you clearly.

None
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:23,240
Dad wanted me to marry Night Immortal,

None
00:39:24,120 --> 00:39:27,200
and Heavenly Emperor also orders me to marry him.

None
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:29,700
I can’t refuse it.

None
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:33,820
If I refuse,

None
00:39:34,600 --> 00:39:36,660
Heavenly Emperor will punish you again,

None
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:39,180
and you have an ambiguous future,

None
00:39:40,200 --> 00:39:42,700
so I can’t be responsible for it.

None
00:39:43,700 --> 00:39:44,860
Anyway,

None
00:39:46,500 --> 00:39:48,320
I won’t let you marry him.

